  "name": "Anndata object of 10x Mouse Brain 5k data set for scDGD training",
  "author": {
    "name": "Viktoria Schuster",
    "givenName": "Viktoria",
    "familyName": "Schuster",
    "@type": "Person"
  },
  "description": "This data from 10x (5k Adult Mouse Brain Nuclei Isolated with Chromium Nuclei Isolation Kit, Single Cell Gene Expression Dataset by Cell Ranger 7.0.0, 2022) is comprised of 7377 cells from the adult mouse brain with 32285 features. Cell type annotations were approximated using CellTpyist with the `Developing_Mouse_Brain` reference model and majority voting. This resulted in 7 distinct cell types.",
